                            <title type="complete" ref="LIT5188MashafaMadbal#PartI" xml:lang="en">
                              The first part of Gubāʿe mǝśṭirāta zamanāt</title>
                            <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                            <note><ref type="mss" corresp="BLorient791"></ref> contains the second part.</note>

                            <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.1">
                              <locus from="2r"></locus>
                              <title type="complete" ref="LIT5188MashafaMadbal#IntroductionI"></title>
                            <incipit xml:lang="gez">በስመ፡ አብ፡ <gap reason="ellipsis"></gap> ንዌጥን፡ በረድኤተ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ወንጽሕፍ፡ መጽሐፈ፡ መድበል፡
                                ዘበትርጓሜሁ፡ጉባዔ፡ ምሥጢራተ፡ ዘመናት፡ ዘገብረ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ በበጊዜሁ፡ቅድመ፡ በዘመነ፡ ብሉይ፡ እስከ፡ ይመጽእ፡ ዘመነ፡ ሐዲስ፡</incipit>
                        </msItem>

                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.2">
                            <locus from="3r" to="184v"/>
                            <title type="complete" ref="LIT5188MashafaMadbal#OldTestament"/>
                            <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                            <incipit xml:lang="gez">ሰላም፡ እብል፡ ለተዋኅዶ፡ ቅድስት፡ ሥላሴ። ቀዊምየ፡ ቅድመ፡ ሥላሴ። እንበለ፡ ናፍቆ፡ አአምን፡ ህላዌ፡
                              ሥላሴ። ግጻዌሆሙ፡ ሥላሴ፤ ወአካሎሙ፡ ሥላሴ። ወቅዳሴሆሙ፡ ከማሁ፡ ሥላሴ።
                            </incipit>

                        </msItem>
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.3">
                          <locus from="184v"></locus>
                          <title type="complete" ref="LIT5188MashafaMadbal#HistoryOfMary" xml:lang="gez"></title>
                          <textLang mainLang="gez"></textLang>
                        </msItem>
                        <colophon xml:id="coloph1">
